#: patterns/faq/accordion-sidebar.php:112
#: patterns/faq/default.php:104
#: patterns/page/home.php:1567
msgid "What is the difference between Templates and Pages?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/accordion-sidebar.php:114
#: patterns/faq/default.php:106
#: patterns/page/home.php:1569
msgid "Pages hold your specific content (like \"About Us\"). Templates define the structure wrapping that content (like headers, sidebars, and footers). Editing a Template affects all Pages that use it."
