#: patterns/faq/accordion-sidebar.php:121
#: patterns/faq/default.php:167
#: patterns/page/home.php:1637
msgid "Does this theme require any plugins?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/accordion-sidebar.php:123
#: patterns/faq/default.php:169
#: patterns/page/home.php:1639
msgid "No. We operate on a strict zero-dependency architecture. Every layout, pattern, and utility is native to the framework, ensuring you never rely on external software to achieve core functionality."
