#: patterns/faq/default.php:140
#: patterns/page/home.php:1607
msgid "How do I set a different template for a specific page?"
msgstr ""

#: patterns/faq/default.php:142
#: patterns/page/home.php:1609
msgid "Inside the page editor, look for the Template setting in the right sidebar (Page tab). Click the template name to swap it (e.g., from \"Default\" to \"Blank Canvas\") or create a new custom one."
